{
  "texts": [
    "To identify the SR33 locus in the contig-level assembly of Ae.",
    "tauschii accession CPI 110799 (the original source of Sr33), we searched for the RGA1e (also known as Sr33) gene sequence (GenBank ID KF031291.1) published by Periyannan et al.",
    "RGA1e gene sequences were also searched against the contig-level assemblies of accessions AUS 18911 (KF031299.1) and AUS 18913 (KF031284.1) 24.",
    "For all accessions, the genes were found within a single contig that located to the chromosome arm 1DS based on the scaffolding against the TA1675 reference assembly.",
    "In the four accessions, we performed BLASTn searches for additional Ae."
  ]
}